=head1 NAME

_FIX_HEADERS_ -- Add readnoise, cpm, pv2_3 to the current file header
the directory

=head1 DESCRIPTION

A number of primitives to add readnoise value, confidence map name and 
pv2_3 to the headers of the current file.

